19
00:00:59,936 --> 00:01:01,856
♪Pretense becomes true as years flow♪

20
00:01:03,424 --> 00:01:09,824
=The Empress Dowager On A Second Spring=

21
00:01:11,120 --> 00:01:11,640
Your Majesty,

22
00:01:12,079 --> 00:01:13,519
Her Majesty is right.

23
00:01:14,040 --> 00:01:16,736
